<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 20:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“确实不合情理”：为什么这位国务院官员因拜登的以色列政策而辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/truly-unconscionable-why-state-department-official-quit-over-bidens-israel-policies/0000018e-a9f9-dc75-afde-f9f935fe0000</link><description>安内尔·谢林是第三位从美国政府辞职的官员，以抗议美国支持以色列对抗加沙哈马斯的战争。她解释了为什么她必须辞职</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/truly-unconscionable-why-state-department-official-quit-over-bidens-israel-policies/0000018e-a9f9-dc75-afde-f9f935fe0000</guid></item><item><title>斋月最后一个星期五，预计将有 100,000 名信徒来到耶路撒冷阿克萨清真寺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/100-000-worshipers-expected-at-jerusalems-al-aqsa-mosque-on-last-friday-of-ramadan/0000018e-aa4e-ddd5-a7ef-afce83270000</link><description>以色列警方正在加强在热点清真寺的警戒，以应对斋月最后一个星期五的祈祷</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:49:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/100-000-worshipers-expected-at-jerusalems-al-aqsa-mosque-on-last-friday-of-ramadan/0000018e-aa4e-ddd5-a7ef-afce83270000</guid></item><item><title>卢旺达、波斯尼亚、乌克兰和现在的哈马斯：10 月 7 日以及世界各地战时性暴力激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/bosnia-ukraine-now-hamas-oct-7-and-the-global-rise-in-wartime-sexual-violence/0000018e-a911-defe-a3ef-bb1d61db0000</link><description>过去30年来，女性的身体日益成为世界各地冲突中的战略目标。尽管哈马斯自 10 月 7 日以来发生的强奸和性侵犯事件令人震惊，但以色列的法医鉴定失败意味着肇事者可能不会被绳之以法</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/bosnia-ukraine-now-hamas-oct-7-and-the-global-rise-in-wartime-sexual-violence/0000018e-a911-defe-a3ef-bb1d61db0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对内塔尼亚胡表示：美国对加沙的政策将取决于以色列减少平民伤害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-netanyahu-u-s-gaza-policy-to-be-based-on-israel-curbing-civilian-harm/0000018e-aa42-ddd5-a7ef-afc27eb00000</link><description>自以色列在加沙发动袭击导致七名世界中央厨房援助人员死亡以来，拜登在首次通话中强调，以色列必须采取具体措施保护加沙平民和援助人员，否则美国对以色列在加沙战争中的支持可能会发生变化</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-netanyahu-u-s-gaza-policy-to-be-based-on-israel-curbing-civilian-harm/0000018e-aa42-ddd5-a7ef-afc27eb00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的爱人和恨者没有从 10 月 7 日和加沙战争中吸取任何教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-lovers-and-haters-have-learnt-nothing-from-oct-7-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-aa15-d906-a5cf-aa95a0790000</link><description>哈马斯袭击和加沙战争应该迫使人们重新思考对以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的信念和恐惧，而不是证明 10 月 6 日持有的严重不足和自私的偏见是正确的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-lovers-and-haters-have-learnt-nothing-from-oct-7-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-aa15-d906-a5cf-aa95a0790000</guid></item><item><title>“为什么以色列害怕半岛电视台？”巴勒斯坦公民批评新法律威胁其广播</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/why-does-israel-fear-al-jazeera-palestinians-in-israel-slam-new-law-threatening-channel/0000018e-a3e6-dd6b-abae-f7e7f28f0000</link><description>对于许多以色列巴勒斯坦公民来说，半岛电视台对占领和加沙战争的报道被认为是必看的节目。一项可能关闭其在以色列业务的新法律引起了愤怒和恐惧</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/why-does-israel-fear-al-jazeera-palestinians-in-israel-slam-new-law-threatening-channel/0000018e-a3e6-dd6b-abae-f7e7f28f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 181 天：拜登和内塔尼亚胡自 3 月中旬以来首次发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-181-biden-netanyahu-speak-for-first-time-since-mid-march/0000018e-aa11-dc75-afde-faf175400001</link><description>以色列军事情报负责人称“未来的日子会很复杂” ■ 以色列国防军向参谋长、国防部长和总理内塔尼亚胡提交有关七名援助人员被杀的初步调查结果 ■ 哈马斯拒绝最新的释放人质/停火协议提议 ■ 拜登和内塔尼亚胡代表发言自 3 月中旬以来的第一次 ■ 战争开始 181 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-181-biden-netanyahu-speak-for-first-time-since-mid-march/0000018e-aa11-dc75-afde-faf175400001</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯拒绝加沙停火提议，称以色列拒绝让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-rejects-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-saying-israel-refuses-to-budge/0000018e-a9b3-d906-a5cf-abb75ce40000</link><description>该组织的黎巴嫩代表表示，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡正在阻止达成协议的谈判取得进展</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:50:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-rejects-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-saying-israel-refuses-to-budge/0000018e-a9b3-d906-a5cf-abb75ce40000</guid></item><item><title>一起我们会赢吗？民意调查显示以色列比以往任何时候都更加分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/together-we-will-win-poll-shows-that-israel-is-more-divided-than-ever/0000018e-a8de-d56e-ad8e-fdfec4680000</link><description>以色列民主研究所表示，哈马斯 10 月 7 日的屠杀和随后发生的加沙战争并未弥合裂痕，但新的社会政治契约仍有希望</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/together-we-will-win-poll-shows-that-israel-is-more-divided-than-ever/0000018e-a8de-d56e-ad8e-fdfec4680000</guid></item><item><title>人权组织称以色列十月份对加沙大楼的袭击造成 106 名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/rights-group-says-israeli-strike-in-october-on-gaza-building-killed-106-palestinians/0000018e-a9a8-dc75-afde-f9f869e30000</link><description>人权观察组织的调查发现，没有证据表明这次袭击针对的是建筑物内的任何武装活动，这构成明显的战争罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/rights-group-says-israeli-strike-in-october-on-gaza-building-killed-106-palestinians/0000018e-a9a8-dc75-afde-f9f869e30000</guid></item><item><title>起步晚，与右翼顾问会面：内塔尼亚胡加沙战争的第一个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/late-starts-meetings-with-right-wing-advisers-netanyahus-first-month-of-the-gaza-war/0000018e-a975-d029-a78f-f9772a390000</link><description>他的日程细节证实了这位总理在加沙冲突初期的表现是多么糟糕。调查结果显示，即使在国家灾难和战争期间，内塔尼亚胡也会在早上相对较晚的时间去上班</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/late-starts-meetings-with-right-wing-advisers-netanyahus-first-month-of-the-gaza-war/0000018e-a975-d029-a78f-f9772a390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人和巴勒斯坦人被指控计划发动袭击并暗杀本格维尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-palestinians-charged-with-plans-to-commit-attacks-assassinate-ben-gvir/0000018e-a982-d906-a5cf-ab9637fb0000</link><description>当局表示，这 10 名被起诉的嫌疑人还计划绑架士兵。在另一起案件中，另外三名以色列人因涉嫌策划袭击耶路撒冷体育场和警察局而被捕</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:13:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-palestinians-charged-with-plans-to-commit-attacks-assassinate-ben-gvir/0000018e-a982-d906-a5cf-ab9637fb0000</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的 42 名以色列人登上福布斯 2024 年世界亿万富豪榜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-42-israelis-feature-on-forbes-world-billionaires-list-for-2024/0000018e-a973-dc69-ad9f-ebffe64c0000</link><description>福布斯榜单上的以色列人数量空前增加（其中包括赌场大亨谢尔登·阿德尔森的遗孀米里亚姆·阿德尔森），这可归因于以色列高科技产业的持续增长</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:45:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-42-israelis-feature-on-forbes-world-billionaires-list-for-2024/0000018e-a973-dc69-ad9f-ebffe64c0000</guid></item><item><title>就像《黑道家族》中的情节一样：这位以色列人在正统暴徒中幸存下来后，将其拍成了电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/just-like-the-sopranos-after-surviving-a-haredi-mob-this-israeli-turned-it-into-a-film/0000018e-a3d3-d222-abef-a7fba4b80000</link><description>本尼·弗雷德曼在耶路撒冷极端正统社区之一开设一家电子产品商店差点丧命。在放弃正统派根源后，他拥抱了对电影的热爱，并带着他的震撼人心的新电影《家》回到了犯罪现场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 13:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/just-like-the-sopranos-after-surviving-a-haredi-mob-this-israeli-turned-it-into-a-film/0000018e-a3d3-d222-abef-a7fba4b80000</guid></item><item><title>我们以色列人必须立即采取行动，结束我们帮助造成的加沙人道主义危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israelis-must-act-now-to-end-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-we-helped-create/0000018e-a416-dd6b-abae-f757969e0000</link><description>加沙的公共卫生灾难对加沙人来说是一场生存危机。如果我们以色列人不开始更清楚地展示我们的人性，如果我们背叛我们自己的基本价值观，那对我们来说也将是灾难性的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israelis-must-act-now-to-end-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-we-helped-create/0000018e-a416-dd6b-abae-f757969e0000</guid></item><item><title>34 岁的利多尔·利维 (Lidor Levy) 在以色列南部恐怖袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/lidor-levy-34-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-a8d1-d40c-adef-fff36d4d0000</link><description>利维是周日甘亚夫内购物中心持刀袭击事件中受伤的三人之一，留下了怀孕的妻子、六个月大的婴儿、父母和两个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/lidor-levy-34-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-a8d1-d40c-adef-fff36d4d0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其航空将所有往返以色列的航班冻结期限延长至 2025 年 3 月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/turkish-airlines-extends-freeze-on-all-flights-to-and-from-israel-until-march-2025/0000018e-a8b2-d801-abce-adf743130000</link><description>国有土耳其航空公司将其特拉维夫航班暂停期延长六个月之际，正值以色列和土耳其之间的外交紧张局势加剧，并且即将迎来以色列最繁忙的旅行季节</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/turkish-airlines-extends-freeze-on-all-flights-to-and-from-israel-until-march-2025/0000018e-a8b2-d801-abce-adf743130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者阻挡警察水枪：“我这样做是为了保护人质的家人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-who-blocked-police-water-canon-i-did-it-to-protect-hostages-families/0000018e-a889-dfed-ad9f-aadbbb110000</link><description>阿隆·格罗佐夫在耶路撒冷总理内塔尼亚胡官邸外举行抗议活动时，爬到警察高压水枪下，获释后对《国土报》表示：“我想到人质遭到虐待，这就是我坚持下去的动力。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-who-blocked-police-water-canon-i-did-it-to-protect-hostages-families/0000018e-a889-dfed-ad9f-aadbbb110000</guid></item><item><title>“我们很遗憾来到这里”：耶路撒冷帐篷营地反内塔尼亚胡抗议的真正含义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-sad-to-be-here-what-the-jerusalem-tent-camp-anti-netanyahu-protest-really-was/0000018e-a486-dd6b-abae-f7c743c30000</link><description>为期四天的集中营呼吁关注加沙人质，在一个晚上与警方发生冲突期间成为头条新闻，但大多数时候，活动人士立即聚集在一起，询问如何不屈服于绝望</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-sad-to-be-here-what-the-jerusalem-tent-camp-anti-netanyahu-protest-really-was/0000018e-a486-dd6b-abae-f7c743c30000</guid></item><item><title>即使在大马士革袭击之后，以色列-伊朗影子战争的游戏规则也没有改变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/rules-of-the-game-in-iranian-shadow-war-are-unchanged-even-after-israels-damascus-attack/0000018e-a840-dd6b-abae-ff431a9e0000</link><description>周一以色列直接袭击伊朗驻大马士革领事馆后，关键问题是伊朗是否会冒着失去与以色列直接对抗的“抵抗轴心”战略的风险，是否会开辟一条针对以色列的直接战线</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/rules-of-the-game-in-iranian-shadow-war-are-unchanged-even-after-israels-damascus-attack/0000018e-a840-dd6b-abae-ff431a9e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>